channel.title: Project #392! Amazing Code Work! ~ Must See ~
channel.description:
[size=36pt]Welcome to Project 392[/size] Poll @ top is if i should release or not!
Before you start wondering there is no #392 protocal this is like a missing link because it jumped from 377-400 so this server will have a little bit of both! (more 377 though since its not full 400 yet!) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Main Goals to Complete; All Skills 80+% by... May 25? 10 Quests by...June 10? (10 Very Hard Quests) Full AutoSpawn-Up to Camelot- by... May 30? Full AutoSpawn-Everything- by... June 15? SkillCape(s)-last priority-by... IDK ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Great Economy - Shops constists of Real RS get things by skills (but some member only shops have good stuff) Kinda Hard Skilling Kinda Hard Money-Making Adding Quests Atm - Integrating Source with SMF! :) - Hardcoded Report System (shows on website aswell) (not done yet though) - started 8:41 A.M 5-5-10 - - Posted 7:15? P.M 5-5-10 - - Range Following - - 5 Quests (about 30 minutes each!) (still adding)- (2 Free to play) (3 Members) - Tutorial Island! (Thanks Spades) - GOT WEBCLIENT TO WORK I WILL ADD PICTURES VERY SOON!
Please Read the Update Log for the full notice on updates (i didnt take pics on everything) (YET) ------------------ Server Main Base: Spades-Scape (I think) Client: Cleaned Deltascape V16 ------FAQ-------- Yellow = Document made while doing it! Red = Update Log Orange = explaining things (what i mean by #392) - at bottom ------Updates Made to Source-------(UpdateLog!)
5-5-10/Re-Wrote: Farming - 75%(so far every seed plants and you recieve correct herb.) 5-5-10/Re-Wrote: Mining - 100% (with -gem- random) 5-5-10/Half-Re-Wrote: Firemaking - 100% (you move south everytime!) 5-5-10/Re-Wrote: Woodcutting - 95% (tree doesn't get removed yet...) 5-5-10/Half-Re-Wrote: Cooking - 100% (you can burn too) 5-5-10/Made From Scratch: Smithing - 50% (Full Bars!) 5-5-10/Range Following! -100% 5-5-10/Swats Emote System - 100% (will not use because this is a 354 source) 5-5-10/Veng!/Veng Other! - 70% (Just Emote will add coding later!) ___________________________________________________________________________________ 5-5-10/Members Items/Places! - 95% (It doesn't say "Members Object" but F2p are only aloud F2p Items while Members have access to Everything! also F2p stops at the falador gates (like real r-s) Mini-games like fight caves are F2p,Fight pits,Pc etc.) (oh forgot to mention that F2p objects go up to Dragon -everything else = Members!) _____ (easily removed though if you want when i release ill have tutorial) ___________________________________________________________________________________ 5-5-10/Skill Menu - 85% (missing Fletching and some skills arent 100% YET!) 5-5-10/Castlewars - 95% (just missing the barricades and door opening and bomb things/timer blinks!) 5-5-10/Re-Wrote-Runecrafting - 100% (tallys everything!) 5-5-10/Started from scratch (cooking on fire) - 10% (shrimps only so far) 5-5-10/Started barrows degrading -8% (just dharoks helm atm) 5-5-10/Writing Hard-Coded Report System! 0% (just started) 5-5-10/Re-Wrote-Crafting! 0% (not tested) 5-5-10/Made From Scratch: Herblore - 1% (just super defence atm...) ________________________________________________________________________________________ 5-6-10/Doubled /Re-Wrote Crafting.Java - 20% (Only Diamond/Ruby/Saphire/Emerald) 5-6-10/Finished Runecrafting.Java -100% (All runes (multiple included) (and pure essence is needed for chaos+) 5-6-10/Agility.Java "Started - 2% (added tiocket exchange can get exp fast that way too!) 5-6-10/Fishing.Java "Started - 0.1% (Just got the code set up nothing is done with this so far.) 5-6-10/You cannot wear hoods into Castle Wars -100% (before it was only cape) 5-6-10/Re-Done Craftinga.Java - 100% (You now can make amulets like real Runescape!) (Pics) 5-6-10/Created Craftingl.Java - 100% (Real Making Leather/Dhide Things! + Shop 100%!) 5-6-10/Smithingb.Java - 100% (Yes fully working) (pic added) 5-6-10/Re-wrote some methods in Smithingb.Java -almost done with smithing! (at a certain lvl you smelt x2,x3 etc. as fast) 5-6-10/Started Construction.Java - 0% (probally wont use construction because it's in 474 cache so dont think it belongs) ________________________________________________________________________________________ 5-7-10/Started Removing Lines from client - 82% -(the not-needed ones everything important is kept) 5-7-10/New Drops! - 99% -(more realistic execpt some monsters drop Tickets/Gems - for the Agility exp shop/ Crafting 5-7-10/No Longer can buy Gems/Bowstring/Armour/Weapons from stores (perfect example of good economy) 5-7-10/Started MiningRune.Java - 70% (Rune essence) (@ level 30 you can mine Pure essence - automatically) ________________________________________________________________________________________ [size=14pt][b]COMPLETE SKILLS (explained)[/b][/size]________________________________________________________________________________________ [b]Crafting![/b] Crafting - 100% - Gem Cutting (all Gems) (all Ammys) (not cut gem and you get the ammy, Real RS style!) Crafting - 100% - Leather (all Dhides) (HardLeather) (CowHide Tanning) (normal Leather) (Thread Dissapearing!) Crafting - 100% - All Emotes Are Correct!________________________________________________________________________________________ [b]Smithing[/b] Smithing - 100% - Ore's on Furnace / my own method x1 ore x2 ore x3 ore x4 ore @ once! (depending on Level) Smithing - 0% - Bar On Anvil / Making things ________________________________________________________________________________________ --------------Pictures (So Far)---------------------
BASIC FILE OUTLINE THING! (WAS REQUESTED) There are more Skills then what are shown (just had to scroll down and got lazy!
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/331hsaw.jpg[/img]
Login Screen -- Not By Me (I just updated the levels before it didnt have a "Member/Donator welcome screen"
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/29arvvm.jpg[/img]
Drinking Potions (from Herblore) -Potions.Java
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/dxmdqc.jpg[/img]
Smithing!
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2925mv9.jpg[/img]
Real Castle Wars (No doors work easy fix though / barricades/bomb things/Timer Blinks Fast ill fix soon) -CastleWars.Java
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/n2bwa0.jpg[/img]
Seeds on Patches!(farming) (and a little note from me about what will happen to cache)-Farming.Java
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/29vkvpg.jpg[/img]
Herbs on Vail! (Herblore) -Herbs.Java
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/slgnth.jpg[/img]
Update System Countdown
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/4kw8bp.jpg[/img]
Just Testing the Firemaking/Woodcutting/Cooking that I Re-Wrote/Started from scratch -Wood.Java -Firemaking.Java - Cooking.Java
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2kk03m.jpg[/img]
Music Really Does Work!
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/14ub0pd.jpg[/img]
Prayer! Interface (from 392) none of that chivalry or W/E
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2igd7p2.jpg[/img]
Crafting (gems to amulet) 95% Like Runescape! (no furnace needed for the amulet mold)
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/68fn7o.jpg[/img]
Skill Tabs! (currently looking for a better interface to put it on!) -SkillT.Java
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/16lzrtf.jpg[/img]
Just because some people like this... (please note this can easily be removed!) I MEANT THE PORT CANT BE CHANGED! SERVER IP CAN!
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/ipnwgm.jpg[/img]
----------------------------------PLEASE NOTE!!!!!!!!!!!!!--------------------------------------------------------- What i mean by this server is #392. I Mean this is Right before they came out with GodWars/Barb. Assault etc. Pretty much the good times. (around 2007ish) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Also I thought it should be different from a #317 or #377 because i re-did the source (Updated some files put in new directory's) - also makes it easier to edit (for me at least) - for example i made a folder "Skills" (where all the Skill.java things are at) and instead of having to search through the client i have everything i need right there by opening one file! -in other words-> this source(files) i made written like half 508 half 377. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Also please note this server can easily be made into a #474 quite easily (i have the 474 cache in a folder called 474 in the client, so if i do release you can just change it like that.) Also please note I have uploaded all the following emotes to the Clean Deltascape V16 thanks to SWAT: Veng Veng Other Rune C'Bow (all) General Graador +Followers (all) (the Npc itself can only be found in the 474 cache unless YOU would download) Sara Boss + Followers (all) (forgot name) Zamorak Boss + Followers (all) (forgot name) Armadyl Boss + Followers (all) Demon (all) Dark Beast (all) 508 Range (all) Dragon Bolts (e) (gfx) (all Runite Bolts pretty much) Veng (the gfx) Veng other (the gfx) all GWD Bosses (Gfx) Wildy Jump (emote) Rest (Real one) (got the Male one only though) and a couple more i cant remember... ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Please note i do NOT use any of these emotes unless they were in the #392 Runescape! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thank-You for reading -Qoodscape -I Gave Creds at Top
